sentences: Olaf Maninger (born 16 October 1964 in Recklinghausen) is a German cellist.
He joined the Berlin Philharmonic in 1994, and was appointed principal cellist with the orchestra in 1996.
In the years 1997 to 2002, Maninger was managing director of the Berliner Philharmoniker GbR (society).
Since the Berliner Philharmoniker Foundation was set up in 2002, he has been a member of the board.
He has been general manager of Berlin Phil Media GmbH since 2008.
